@startuml Complete_Project_Architecture
title STM32F407 Bare-Metal C++ Drivers — Complete Project Architecture (up to v0.8.0)

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam rectangle {
    BackgroundColor #F5FAFF
    BorderColor #2C7FB8
    ArrowColor #2C7FB8
}
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

package "Toolchain" {
  rectangle "STM32CubeIDE / GCC ARM\nOpenOCD + GDB" as TOOLCHAIN
}

package "Repository: stm32f407-baremetal-cpp-drivers" {

  package "Startup" {
    rectangle "startup_stm32f407vgtx.s\n(vector table, Reset_Handler)" as STARTUP
  }

  package "Linker" {
    rectangle "STM32F407VGTX_FLASH.ld\nSTM32F407VGTX_RAM.ld" as LINKER
  }

  package "Drivers/Drivers" {
    rectangle "Inc/*.h + Src/*.cpp\nGPIO · RCC · EXTI · NVIC\nSysTick · USART · SPI · I2C" as DRIVERS
  }

  package "Drivers/Applications" {
    rectangle "Example apps\n(one active main() at a time)" as APPS
  }

  package "Docs" {
    rectangle "GPIO.md · RCC.md · USART.md\nSPI.md · I2C.md · CAN.md" as DOCS_MD
    rectangle "puml/\n(this diagram set)" as DOCS_PUML
  }
}

package "Hardware" {
  rectangle "STM32F407VG Discovery\n(ARM Cortex-M4)" as BOARD
  rectangle "ST-Link V2" as STLINK
}

TOOLCHAIN --> DRIVERS : compiles
TOOLCHAIN --> APPS : compiles
STARTUP --> DRIVERS : calls main() after\nreset & static init
LINKER --> STARTUP : places .isr_vector,\n.text, .data, .bss

APPS --> DRIVERS : uses driver API
DRIVERS --> BOARD : direct register I/O
TOOLCHAIN --> STLINK : flash + debug
STLINK --> BOARD : SWD

DOCS_MD ..> DRIVERS : documents
DOCS_PUML ..> DRIVERS : documents

note bottom of DRIVERS
  Six drivers released through v0.6.0
  (GPIO, RCC, EXTI, NVIC, SysTick, USART).
  SPI added in v0.7.0, I2C in v0.8.0 —
  all register-level, no HAL/LL.
end note

@enduml
